title: Kamp Koral: SpongeBob's Under Years
overview: Kamp Koral: SpongeBob's Under Years introduces 10-year-old SpongeBob SquarePants during his summer at sleepaway camp. In the series, SpongeBob and his pals spend the summer building underwater campfires, catching wild jellyfish, and swimming in Lake Yuckymuck at the craziest camp in the kelp forest, Kamp Koral.
